# UI Component Patterns

## Layout Structure
- Use `min-h-screen bg-background` for full-page layouts
- Center content with `max-w-4xl mx-auto`
- Use `space-y-6` for consistent vertical spacing
- Group related sections with `Card` components

## Form Patterns
- Use `Label` components with `htmlFor` attributes
- Implement proper input validation and error states
- Use `disabled` prop for loading states
- Handle Enter key press for form submission

## Status Indicators
- Use `Badge` components for status display
- Implement loading spinners: `animate-spin h-3 w-3 border-2 border-current border-t-transparent rounded-full`
- Use semantic colors: `text-green-600`, `text-red-600`, `text-blue-500`
- Show/hide elements conditionally with `{condition && <Component />}`

## Chat Interface
- Use flexbox for message alignment: `justify-end` for user, `justify-start` for system
- Implement message bubbles with rounded corners
- Show timestamps and status icons
- Use `overflow-y-auto` for scrollable chat containers

## Button Patterns
- Use `variant="outline"` for secondary actions
- Use `size="sm"` for compact buttons
- Group related buttons with `flex flex-wrap gap-2`
- Disable buttons during loading states

## Debug Information
- Use `font-mono` for technical data display
- Group debug info in collapsible sections
- Use muted colors for secondary information
- Provide troubleshooting steps in user-friendly format
